	<div class="atmos-banner atmos-banner--button atmos-banner--tourism section--shadow--both" style=" background-image: url('https://2019.fluufff.org/website/assets/images/hotel/tourism-1.jpg');">
		<p class="text fs--18 white center">
			At only 700m of the hotel, there's the <strong>Sealife Center</strong>! <br/>A small zoo for sea creatures and a rescue centre for seals!		</p>
		<a href="https://www.visitsealife.com/blankenberge/en/" class="resetlink link-button link-button--white fs--16 m-t-24" title="Sealife Blankenberge">			<span>Discover Sealife Center</span><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>		</a>	</div>
